             function validateEmail(email) {
                 var re = /^(([^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+(\.[^<>()[\]\\.,;:\s@\"]+)*)|(\".+\"))@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\])|(([a-zA-Z\-0-9]+\.)+[a-zA-Z]{2,}))$/;
                 return re.test(email);
             }
 
             function getSelectedText(elementId) {
                 var elt = document.getElementById(elementId);
 
                 if (elt.selectedIndex == -1)
                     return null;
 
                 return elt.options[elt.selectedIndex].text;
             }
 
             // Get the total seconds elapsed from the server.
             function getSessionTime(secondsElapsedFromServer) {
                 if (secondsElapsedFromServer == "") {
                     // this is their first page load of the session
                     secondsElapsed = 0;
                 } else {
                     secondsElapsed = secondsElapsedFromServer;
                 }
             }
 
 $(document).ready(function () {

             hasSeenPopup = false,

                 hasSeenPopup = true;

             if (document.getElementById("hfUserAlreadyRegisteredMC").value == 'TRUE'){
                 Cookies.set('dontShowNewsletterPopup', 'true');
             }
             if (Cookies.get('dontShowNewsletterPopup') == 'true') {
                 dontShowNewsletterPopup = true;
             }
             
 
             if (Cookies.get('hasSeenNewsletterPopup') == 'true') {
                 hasSeenNewsletterPopup = true;
                 // Take the current date and subtract the number of miliseconds in 30 days (30*86400)*1000.
                 if ( (currentDate - ((30 * 86400)*1000)) > Cookies.get('sawNewsletterPopup') ) {
                     hasSeenNewsletterPopup = false;
                 }
                 // Testing

                 //    hasSeenNewsletterPopup = false;
                 //}
             }
 
             
 
             // Testing - ouput the data

             //console.log("hfUserAlreadyRegisteredMC: " + document.getElementById("hfUserAlreadyRegisteredMC").value);
 
 
                 // Count the seconds up, manage the popup, and set cookies.
                 function countTimer() {
                     // count the seconds up by 1
                     secondsElapsed++;
 
                     // Survey popup

 //mixpanel.track("Survey Popup Displayed");
                         // set our variable to show they've seen the popup
   //                      hasSeenPopup = true;
     //                }
 
                     // Newsletter popup
                     // check if 10 seconds have gone by and if they haven't
                     // seen the popup
                     if (secondsElapsed >= 10 && hasSeenNewsletterPopup == false) {
                         // start the popup
                         $('#newsletterModal').fadeIn(200);
                         $('.modal-overlay').fadeIn(200);
                         mixpanel.track("Newsletter Popup Displayed");
                         // set our variable to show they've seen the popup
                         hasSeenNewsletterPopup = true;
                     }
                 }
 
                 // Survey
                 // Check if they've seen the popup.  If they have, don't bother running
                 // the javascript counter
 
                 
 
                 //if (hasSeenPopup == false && document.getElementById("HFPopUpSurveyActive").value == 'TRUE') {
                 //    // Run the countTimer function every second after the page loads,
                 //    // as long as they haven't seen the popup.
                 //    setInterval(countTimer, 1000);
                 //}
 
                 // Newsletter
                 if (hasSeenNewsletterPopup == false && document.getElementById("hfUserAlreadyRegisteredMC").value == 'FALSE' && dontShowNewsletterPopup == false) {
                     // Run the countTimer function every second after the page loads,
                     // as long as they haven't seen the popup.
                     setInterval(countTimer, 1000);
                 }

                 // Handle the newsletter modal dismissal
                 $('.btn-modal-newsletter-dismiss, .modal-overlay').click(function (event) {
 
                     if ($(this).attr('id') == "btnNewsletterModalDismiss") {
                         event.preventDefault();
                     }
 
                     $('#newsletterModal').fadeOut(200);
                     $('.modal-overlay').fadeOut(200);
 
                     // set the cookie that says they have seen the popup
                     Cookies.set('hasSeenNewsletterPopup', 'true');
                     Cookies.set('sawNewsletterPopup', d.getTime());
 
                     // set our variable to show they've seen the popup
                     hasSeenNewsletterPopup = true;
                 });
 
                 $('.btn-newsletter-cta').click(function (event) {
                     var allValid = true;
 
                     var name = $('.newsletter-name').val();
                     var org = $('.newsletter-org').val();
                     var state = $('.newsletter-state option:selected').html();
                     var email = $('.newsletter-email').val();
                     var country = $('.newsletter-country option:selected').html();
 
                     // Validate the data
                     if ( name == "" ) {
                         event.preventDefault();
                         $('.helper-name').show();
                         allValid = false;
                     }
                     if (org == "") {
                         event.preventDefault();
                         $('.helper-org').show();
                         allValid = false;
                     }
                     if (email == "") {
                         event.preventDefault();
                         $('.helper-email').show();
                         allValid = false;
                     }
                     if (country == "United States" && state == "Select a State") {
                         event.preventDefault();
                         $('.helper-state').show();
                         allValid = false;
                     }
                     if ( email != "" ) {
                         if ( validateEmail(email) == false ) {
                             event.preventDefault();
                             $('.helper-email').show();
                             allValid = false;
                         }
                     }
 
                     if ( allValid == true ) {
                         // Validation passed.
                         mixpanel.track('Newsletter Popup Submitted');
                         Cookies.set('dontShowNewsletterPopup', 'true');
                     }
                 });
 
             });
